    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s still got that spotless, fresh feel inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for its next big adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
