    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade vehicle, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features original, deep-gloss paint with zero swirl marks or stone chips, recently protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the finish glow. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is completely free of sun damage, fading, or rattles. Mechanically, this car is flawless, having been serviced exclusively at certified dealerships with a comprehensive binder of service records included in the sale. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. It has been strictly garage-kept under a soft cover and has never seen rain or snow. If you are looking for the absolute finest example of this model currently on the market, this is it.",
